				            <div id="mID2960" class="desktopmodules_htmldocument_htmlmodule_ascx"><div class="ag"><h2>The Vistas – Senior Assisted Living</h2><img class="picl" src="../../Portals/_ExpressSite/images/assisted_living.jpg">

<p>Located on the second floor for <a href="../377/photo_gallery.aspx"><strong>Laurel Parc</strong></a>, you will find The Vistas, <strong>Laurel Parc’s</strong> very own licensed <a href="../376/campus_amenities.aspx"><strong>senior assisted living community</strong></a>.</p>

<p>All <strong>senior assisted living services</strong> at <strong>The Vistas</strong> are planned with the understanding that residents individual needs can change over time. In planning and providing services we always  consider the unique interests, attributes, abilities and overall health status of each resident. Residents are always  encouraged to perform as many of their activities of daily living as they are  able.</p>

<p>Resident service plans are created and reviewed on a regular  basis with the involvement of each resident, family members and key staff  members to ensure the appropriateness of the direction, scope and degree of the  services being provided.</p>

<p><strong>Assisted living services</strong> at <strong>The Vistas Assisted Living</strong> are supervised by a licensed nurse and which may include medication monitoring, grooming and bathing assistance, personal laundry and other assistance with the activities of daily living.  </p>

<p>Charges for individual personal care service plans are  determined through an assessment process using a point based scoring  method.  Points are determined by the frequency and duration of your individual service needs, as well as direct and  indirect cost of performing the service. The assessment will reflect a point total and total charge for the services provided</p>

<p><strong>You may add, cancel, or modify services as your needs  change. Best of all, you pay for only the services you needed. This approach most accurately ensures that the charge for care services fees directly reflects your personal and individual service needs.</strong></p>

<img class="picr" src="../../Portals/_ExpressSite/images/assisted_living2.jpg">

<p>Your basic monthly charge includes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Scheduled Transportation</li>
  <li>Activities and community life enrichment</li>
  <li>Wellness program, and ongoing needs assessment</li>
  <li>Availability of dining, housekeeping, and laundry needs</li>
  <li>Use of all common areas and community amenities
     <ul>
       <li>Theatre</li>
       <li>Exercise facility</li>
       <li>Lounge</li>
       <li>Bistro</li>
       <li>Activities and Game Room</li>
       <li>Conservatory</li>
       <li>Patio</li>
     </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Off street parking</li>
</ul>

<p>Your Apartment Home Features:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Three meals and snacks daily served in our community dining room</li>
  <li>Emergency call system</li>
  <li>Availability of 24 hour personal care</li>
  <li>All utilities including phone</li>
  <li>Generous closet space</li>
  <li>Basic cable service</li>
  <li>Private mailbox</li>
  <li>Weekly housekeeping and linen service</li>
  <li>Complimentary Wireless Internet</li>
</ul>
</div></div>
				            
